TxOp Timeout Module¶

txop_timeout.py

Data object representing timeout. According to Mdl documentation, this value must be in the range of [0, 255]. https://git.isis.vanderbilt.edu/SwRI/mdl-archive/blob/master/spec/MDL_v1_0_0.xsd Author: Tameem Samawi (tsamawi@cra.com)
